data.description: This February fall in love with your very own Steel Creek here at Sun City Peachtree! This home is loaded with options: Open kitchen with huge island that has a great breakfast bar and offers tons of prep space. Kitchen has white cabinets that are staggered, along with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The home has clean site lines to the dining are and gathering room. Also, there is a sunroom to enjoy brisk mornings and cool evenings in. Plus, all the windows are cased, and in the garage a set of pull downstairs to storage.
